Name: Stardew Sweet
Age: 19
Species: Unicorn
Gender: Male
Pronouns: he/they/it

Past: Stardew was born blind in one eye, but can see perfectly fine with the other. He was raised by his aunt and uncle ever since he was a child ever since his parents died in a flying accident.

Appearance: Stardew has dull blue fur with assorted white spots. He has a black mane with white streaks that's curly on his head and straight down his back. He has brown eyes but one of his eyes are completely white due to being blind in one eye. He has wings that are the same color as his fur. They have some freckles on their face and a white horn. Stardew wears two black hair clips to keep his hair out of his eyes. He has a septum piercing as well. His cutie mark is a mushroom which symbolizes his talent in growing fungi and other plants as well. He has eye bags from a heavy lack of sleep.

Personality: Stardew is very carefree and laid-back, rarely ever worrying about things. He keeps an upbeat and positive attitude. He can be reckless, causing Onyx to worry and always feeling bad that he worries Onyx. Stardew struggles with low self-esteem , often prioritizing others over himself. He's very loyal, even if he's clumsy and a little dumb sometimes. He'll always come through in the end to help someone he cares about.

Other: He uses a tranquilizer gun he stole from a lab as a weapon and wears brass knuckles on his hooves, as well as a dagger. His magic is best in defensive, practical, and light spells.
